    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a peerless 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) that defines showroom condition. Powered by the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, this naturally aspirated powerplant exhibits flawless compression and peak volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for razor-sharp damping and a mechanical locking rear differential for superior corner-exit traction. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the undercarriage remains free of oxidation, and the DME report confirms zero over-rev occurrences. With factory-original paint depth and an interior devoid of bolster wear or UV degradation, this is a museum-grade example for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
